text: Oumou Touré (born February 18, 1988) is a Senegalese basketball player. She represented Senegal in the basketball competition at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:Senegalese women's basketball players Category:Basketball players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic basketball players of Senegal Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Senegalese expatriate basketball people in France Category:Centers (basketball)
